stream
BT /F2 14 Tf 54 712.0 Td (UNDERSTANDING YOUR AUTISTIC CHILD) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 690.0 Td (Autism is a neurological DIFFERENCE, not a deficiency.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 676.0 Td (Your child experiences the world more intensely - sounds louder,) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 662.0 Td (lights brighter, textures sharper, social rules more confusing.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 638.2 Td (KEY PRINCIPLES:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 624.2 Td (- Presume competence - they understand more than they can express) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 610.2 Td (- Behavior IS communication - look for the unmet need) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 596.2 Td (- Accommodate first, then teach - reduce barriers before adding demands) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 582.2 Td (- Special interests are STRENGTHS - use them to teach other skills) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 568.2 Td (- Meltdowns are NOT tantrums - they are nervous system overload) Tj ET
endstream
endobj
