BT /F2 14 Tf 54 712.0 Td (SENSORY DIET PLANNER) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 690.0 Td (A sensory diet provides regular sensory input throughout the day) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 676.0 Td (to keep your child regulated. Work with an OT to customize.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 648.2 Td (CALMING \(when overstimulated\):) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 632.2 Td (- Deep pressure \(weighted blanket, tight hugs, compression vest\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 618.2 Td (- Dim lights / reduce noise) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 604.2 Td (- Slow rhythmic movement \(rocking, swinging\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 590.2 Td (- Chewing \(chewy tube, crunchy snacks\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 576.2 Td (- Warm bath or shower) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 558.2 Td (ALERTING \(when under-responsive\):) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 542.2 Td (- Cold water or ice) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 528.2 Td (- Fast movement \(jumping, spinning, running\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 514.2 Td (- Bright lights or music) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 500.2 Td (- Sour or spicy flavors) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 486.2 Td (- Vibration \(vibrating toothbrush, massager\)) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 468.2 Td (ORGANIZING \(for focus\):) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 452.2 Td (- Heavy work \(carrying books, pushing cart, digging\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 438.2 Td (- Oral motor \(drinking through straw, blowing bubbles\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 424.2 Td (- Fidget tools \(putty, tangle, stress ball\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 410.2 Td (- Proprioceptive input \(wall push-ups, bear walks\)) Tj ET
endstream
endobj
