BT /F2 14 Tf 54 712.0 Td (COMMUNICATION SUPPORT) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 686.0 Td (If your child is verbal but struggles:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 670.0 Td (- Give processing time \(wait 10+ seconds after asking\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 656.0 Td (- Use visual supports alongside verbal instructions) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 642.0 Td (- One instruction at a time \(not multi-step\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 628.0 Td (- Be literal \(avoid sarcasm, idioms, implied meaning\)) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 610.0 Td (If your child is non-speaking or limited verbal:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 594.0 Td (- AAC \(communication device\) is NOT a last resort - offer early) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 580.0 Td (- Honor ALL forms of communication \(gesture, picture, behavior\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 566.0 Td (- Don't withhold AAC to 'encourage' speech) Tj ET
